flowchart LR
    C[Client] --> A[Admission Control]
    A --> CA[Cache]
    CA -- Hit --> C
    CA -- Miss --> R[Shard Router]

    R -. route epoch .-> M[(Metadata Service)]
    R --> PA[Pool: Shard A Primary]
    R --> RA[Pool: Shard A Replica]
    R --> PB[Pool: Shard B Primary]
    R --> RB[Pool: Shard B Replica]

    PA --> AP[(Shard A Primary)]
    RA --> AR[(Shard A Replica)]
    PB --> BP[(Shard B Primary)]
    RB --> BR[(Shard B Replica)]

    AP -- Physical WAL --> AR
    BP -- Physical WAL --> BR

    AP --> OA[(Outbox)]
    OA --> CDC[CDC / Reshard Worker]
    CDC --> BP

    AP --> OBS[Metrics / Logs / Traces]
    BP --> OBS
    R --> OBS
    M --> OBS
